{"title":"MSc in Experiential Digital Marketing Communications (XDMarComs)","markdown":{"yaml":{"format":"html"},"headingText":"MSc in Experiential Digital Marketing Communications (XDMarComs)","headingAttr":{"id":"","classes":["center"],"keyvalue":[]},"containsRefs":false,"markdown":"\n\n<style>\n.center {\n  text-align: center;\n}\n\n.logo {\n  width: 300px;\n  border-radius: 30px;\n  display: block;\n  margin: 0 auto;\n}\n\n.flex-container {\n  display: flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  justify-content: space-between;\n  margin-top: 30px;\n}\n\n.text {\n  width: 70%;\n  text-align: justify;\n}\n\n.side-image {\n  width: 200px;\n  border-radius: 10px;\n  margin-left: 30px;\n}\n\n.footer {\n  text-align: center;\n  font-size: 0.9em;\n  margin-top: 30px;\n  color: #777;\n  \n}\n\n.footer a {\n  color: #16537e;\n  text-decoration: none;\n}\n\nh2, h3 {\n  text-align: left;\n}\n\np {\n  text-align: justify;\n}\n\n.blue-title {\n  color: #16537e;\n}\n</style>\n\n\n## Master the Future of Marketing {.center}\n\n<div class=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"images/logomaster.jpg\" class=\"logo\">\n</div>\n\n---\n\n<div class=\"flex-container\">\n<div class=\"text\">\n\n**Purpose:**  \nTo empower ambitious students and professionals to master digital storytelling, navigate the data-driven marketing landscape, and lead brands in delivering meaningful, memorable experiences to the connected consumer.\n\n</div>\n<div>\n  <img src=\"images/pic1.jpg\" class=\"side-image\">\n</div>\n</div>\n\n---\n\n<div class=\"flex-container\">\n<div class=\"text\">\n\n**Mission:**  \nTo foster a student-centric, innovation-driven learning environment where individuals thrive academically, professionally, and personally.\n\n**We empower our students with:**\n\n- Advanced skills in AI, data analytics, IoT, and phygital marketing  \n- Essential soft skills such as adaptability, agility, resilience, and collaboration  \n- The capacity to create sustainable value in an ever-evolving digital landscape  \n\n</div>\n<div>\n  <img src=\"images/pic2.jpg\" class=\"side-image\">\n</div>\n</div>\n\n## What Sets Our Programme Apart\n\n<h3 class=\"blue-title\">Flexible Delivery Structure</h3>\n\nXDMarComs offers a flexible, hybrid learning programme with intensive five-week modules. Combining weekend classes, online seminars, and self-paced content, it supports professionals in balancing work with academic growth.\n\n<h3 class=\"blue-title\">Integrated Cross-Disciplinary Framework</h3>\n\nExcellence in modern marketing demands a multidisciplinary approach. Our curriculum integrates technology, psychology, analytics, design, consumer culture, and communication to equip graduates with strategic, cross-functional solutions.\n\n<h3 class=\"blue-title\">Continuous Professional Development</h3>\n\nBeyond career advancement, the programme cultivates self-directed learning and metacognitive skills, empowering graduates to adapt and grow continuously in evolving digital marketing landscapes.\n\n---\n\n<div class=\"footer\">\n  © 2025 xdmarcoms. All rights reserved. | <a href=\"#\">Privacy Policy</a> | <a href=\"#\">Terms of Service</a>\n</div>\n","srcMarkdownNoYaml":"\n\n<style>\n.center {\n  text-align: center;\n}\n\n.logo {\n  width: 300px;\n  border-radius: 30px;\n  display: block;\n  margin: 0 auto;\n}\n\n.flex-container {\n  display: flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  justify-content: space-between;\n  margin-top: 30px;\n}\n\n.text {\n  width: 70%;\n  text-align: justify;\n}\n\n.side-image {\n  width: 200px;\n  border-radius: 10px;\n  margin-left: 30px;\n}\n\n.footer {\n  text-align: center;\n  font-size: 0.9em;\n  margin-top: 30px;\n  color: #777;\n  \n}\n\n.footer a {\n  color: #16537e;\n  text-decoration: none;\n}\n\nh2, h3 {\n  text-align: left;\n}\n\np {\n  text-align: justify;\n}\n\n.blue-title {\n  color: #16537e;\n}\n</style>\n\n# MSc in Experiential Digital Marketing Communications (XDMarComs) {.center}\n\n## Master the Future of Marketing {.center}\n\n<div class=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"images/logomaster.jpg\" class=\"logo\">\n</div>\n\n---\n\n<div class=\"flex-container\">\n<div class=\"text\">\n\n**Purpose:**  \nTo empower ambitious students and professionals to master digital storytelling, navigate the data-driven marketing landscape, and lead brands in delivering meaningful, memorable experiences to the connected consumer.\n\n</div>\n<div>\n  <img src=\"images/pic1.jpg\" class=\"side-image\">\n</div>\n</div>\n\n---\n\n<div class=\"flex-container\">\n<div class=\"text\">\n\n**Mission:**  \nTo foster a student-centric, innovation-driven learning environment where individuals thrive academically, professionally, and personally.\n\n**We empower our students with:**\n\n- Advanced skills in AI, data analytics, IoT, and phygital marketing  \n- Essential soft skills such as adaptability, agility, resilience, and collaboration  \n- The capacity to create sustainable value in an ever-evolving digital landscape  \n\n</div>\n<div>\n  <img src=\"images/pic2.jpg\" class=\"side-image\">\n</div>\n</div>\n\n## What Sets Our Programme Apart\n\n<h3 class=\"blue-title\">Flexible Delivery Structure</h3>\n\nXDMarComs offers a flexible, hybrid learning programme with intensive five-week modules. Combining weekend classes, online seminars, and self-paced content, it supports professionals in balancing work with academic growth.\n\n<h3 class=\"blue-title\">Integrated Cross-Disciplinary Framework</h3>\n\nExcellence in modern marketing demands a multidisciplinary approach. Our curriculum integrates technology, psychology, analytics, design, consumer culture, and communication to equip graduates with strategic, cross-functional solutions.\n\n<h3 class=\"blue-title\">Continuous Professional Development</h3>\n\nBeyond career advancement, the programme cultivates self-directed learning and metacognitive skills, empowering graduates to adapt and grow continuously in evolving digital marketing landscapes.\n\n---\n\n<div class=\"footer\">\n  © 2025 xdmarcoms. All rights reserved. | <a href=\"#\">Privacy Policy</a> | <a href=\"#\">Terms of Service</a>\n</div>\n"},"formats":{"html":{"identifier":{"display-name":"HTML","target-format":"html","base-format":"html"},"execute":{"fig-width":7,"fig-height":5,"fig-format":"retina","fig-dpi":96,"df-print":"default","error":false,"eval":true,"cache":null,"freeze":false,"echo":true,"output":true,"warning":true,"include":true,"keep-md":false,"keep-ipynb":false,"ipynb":null,"enabled":null,"daemon":null,"daemon-restart":false,"debug":false,"ipynb-filters":[],"ipynb-shell-interactivity":null,"plotly-connected":true,"engine":"markdown"},"render":{"keep-tex":false,"keep-typ":false,"keep-source":false,"keep-hidden":false,"prefer-html":false,"output-divs":true,"output-ext":"html","fig-align":"default","fig-pos":null,"fig-env":null,"code-fold":"none","code-overflow":"scroll","code-link":false,"code-line-numbers":false,"code-tools":false,"tbl-colwidths":"auto","merge-includes":true,"inline-includes":false,"preserve-yaml":false,"latex-auto-mk":true,"latex-auto-install":true,"latex-clean":true,"latex-min-runs":1,"latex-max-runs":10,"latex-makeindex":"makeindex","latex-makeindex-opts":[],"latex-tlmgr-opts":[],"latex-input-paths":[],"latex-output-dir":null,"link-external-icon":false,"link-external-newwindow":false,"self-contained-math":false,"format-resources":[],"notebook-links":true},"pandoc":{"standalone":true,"wrap":"none","default-image-extension":"png","to":"html","css":["styles.css"],"toc":true,"output-file":"index.html"},"language":{"toc-title-document":"Table of contents","toc-title-website":"On this page","related-formats-title":"Other Formats","related-notebooks-title":"Notebooks","source-notebooks-prefix":"Source","other-links-title":"Other Links","code-links-title":"Code Links","launch-dev-container-title":"Launch Dev Container","launch-binder-title":"Launch Binder","article-notebook-label":"Article Notebook","notebook-preview-download":"Download Notebook","notebook-preview-download-src"